</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">进出口有限公司、广东博罗远航实业有限公司、博罗县宏宇通讯工程构件厂。</span></span></span></span></p>',1186142381859,'',NULL,0,NULL,31,'严家成','惠州市光速通信工程有限公司','',NULL,10000,NULL,0,'0',NULL,NULL,'惠州市光速通信工程有限公司','惠州市光速通信工程有限公司','',1219106987015,NULL,9,'惠州市光速通信工程有限公司',4,2,NULL,'YANJIACHENG@WEAFORCE.COM',1251943398087,'0','ACALEPH8@YAHOO.COM.CN',NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(98,'200','<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">&mdash;&mdash;公司成立以来，办公场所先后因租房搬迁了三次，尽管面积一次比一次大，但由于不是自己的物业，办公条件受到很大限制。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体\">2006</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">年初，公司耗资数百万元，在博罗县城购买了一幢办公大楼，进行了全面装修，添置了办公设备，办公条件才实现了质和量的飞跃。现在，公司办公楼大院占地面积近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体\">4000</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-f